info.author: Akhil Lawrence
info.description:
**Blood Donors Directory**

[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/akhilputhiry/blood-donors-directory.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/akhilputhiry/blood-donors-directory) [![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/blood-donors-directory.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/blood-donors-directory)

Many colleges and organizations are having blood donors forum/group within their organization these days. This project is a small application intented to help these organization in maintaining their database.

Features:
* Donor database
* Donor search
* Donation register
* Post donation requests in social media/organizations pages
